ZH: 我们必须赶快完成这项任务。
EN: We must quickly finish this task.

ZH: 开车的时候必须系安全带。
EN: You must wear a seatbelt when driving.

ZH: 在中国，学生必须穿校服上学。
EN: In China, students must wear uniforms to school.

ZH: 为了保护环境，我们必须减少使用塑料袋。
EN: To protect the environment, we must reduce our use of plastic bags.

ZH: 为了健康，每天必须喝足够的水。
EN: For health reasons, you must drink enough water every day.

ZH: 在考试中，你必须自己动手做题。
EN: In exams, you must solve the questions by yourself.

ZH: 老师说了，你必须把这本书读完。
EN: The teacher said you must finish reading this book.

ZH: 大家都知道，健康需要坚持锻炼，这是必须的。
EN: Everyone knows that regular exercise is a must for good health.

ZH: 为了顺利毕业，必须通过所有考试。
EN: In order to graduate successfully, you must pass all exams.

ZH: 念书时必须静心。
EN: You must concentrate while studying.

ZH: 防晒霜是夏天游泳时必须的。
EN: Sunscreen is a must for swimming in the summer.

ZH: 在这个工作中, 你必须掌握各种技能。
EN: In this job, you must have a variety of skills.

ZH: 为了安全，你必须关上门。
EN: For safety, you must close the door.

ZH: 参加活动的学生必须提前报名。
EN: Students who want to participate in the activity must register in advance.

ZH: 学乐器的时候，你必须用心练习。
EN: When learning an instrument, you must practice diligently.

ZH: 总结今天的活动是必须的。
EN: Summarizing today's activities is a must.

ZH: 在这项工作中，团队合作是必须的。
EN: Teamwork is a must in this job.

ZH: 外出旅游时，必须随身携带身份证。
EN: When traveling, you must carry your ID with you.

ZH: 为了家人，你必须努力奋斗。
EN: For your family, you must strive hard.

ZH: 这个组织的成员必须遵守规定。
EN: Members of this organization must follow the rules.
